      </p>
    </div>
    <table id="ECR">
      <!-- Your HTML table content -->
    </table>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
```

Make sure to include the `xlsx.core.min.js` and `xlsx.export.min.js` files in the same directory as your HTML file. When you load the HTML page, it will automatically trigger the `table2Excel` function, which will convert the table to an Excel file and initiate the download.

